                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps123">Mazmura Dāwit: Psalmus 123</title>
                           <note>The text is preceded by the following indication: <q xml:lang="gez">በመሐት<supplied reason="omitted">ወ፡</supplied> ፋሲካ፡</q>.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.3">
                           <locus target="#17v"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4268Tazakkar">ሊጦን፡ ዘዓርብ፡</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.4">
                           <locus from="17v" to="18r"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4271Prayer">ሊጦን፡ ዘሠርክ፡</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.5">
                           <locus from="18r" to="18v"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4245Prayer">ሊጦን፡ ዘሠር<supplied reason="omitted">ክ፡</supplied> ዘዘወትር፨</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ወካዕበ፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅዝ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> እስመ፡ ረሰየ፡ ለነ፡ ተድላ፡
                           </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.6">
                           <locus target="#18v"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4263Prayer">ሊጦን፡ ዘአር<supplied reason="omitted">ብ</supplied>፡</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅዝ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> እንዘ፡ <sic>ነአኵቶ፡</sic> በኵሉ፡ 
                              ወውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ እስመ፡ ከደነነ፡ ወረድአነ፨ ዓቀበነ፡ ወአብጽሐነ፡ እስከ፡ ዛቲ፡ ሰአት፡
                           </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.7">
                           <locus from="18v" to="20v"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#BaendaEllaNomu4">ሊጦን፡ <choice><sic>ዘመታ፡</sic><corr resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices">ዘሙታን፡</corr></choice></title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ወካዕበ፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ በል፨ እግዚ<supplied reason="explanation">አ፡</supplied> ሕያዋን፡ ወሕይወተ፡ ሙታን፡ ተስፋ፡ ቅቡፃን፡ ረዳኤ፡ ምንዱባን፡ ወመንጽሔ፡ 
                              ኃጥአን፡ ዘሞተ፡ አጽራዕከ፡ ወማዕሠረ፡ ሰይጣን፡ በቲከከ፡ ሕይወት፡ <sic>ለትዝምድ፡</sic> ሰብእ፡
                           </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.8">
                           <locus from="20v" to="21r"/>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#SuppMasqal">ሊጦን፡ ዘመ<supplied reason="omitted">ስ</supplied>ቀል፨</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ወካዕ<supplied reason="omitted">በ</supplied>፡ ናስተበቍዕ፡ ለዕፀ፡ መስቀል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጽኑዓ፡ ሥልጣን፡ ወኃይል፡ ወሊሉየ፡ መልክዕ፨
                           </incipit>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="21r" to="50v"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1960Mashaf#SerataQeddase">Ordinary of the Mass</title>                        
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#21r"/>
                           በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ንጽሕፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ከመ፡ ይበሉ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ወዲያቆን፡ ወሕዝብ፡ ወኵሉ፡ 
                           ዘመፍትው፡ በበጊዜሁ፡ በከመ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቅዱሳን፡
                        </incipit>
                        <note>The Ordinary of the Mass is separated from the anaphoras, like in recent manuscripts.
                           The text bears a second title after the prayers for the blessing of the tools for the Eucharist:
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/> ሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ ዘይደሉ፡ ለቀሲስ፡ ወለዲያቆን፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ወኵሉ፡ 
                              ዘመፍትው፡ በበጊዜሁ፡ በከመ፡ አበዊነ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ግብጻውያን፡ 
                           </q>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     
