                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7.13">
                           <locus from="138v" to="147v"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1098Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-Bāsǝlyos</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ዘበዓለ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ይቀድስ፡ ለእመ፡ ሀሎ፡ ካህን፡ ዘየዓቢ፡ በላዕለ፡ ካህን፡ ቀዊሞ፨ አኰቴተ፡ ቍርባን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ በስልዮስ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted" resp="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/>
                           </incipit>
                           <note>
                              According to the incipit, the anaphora is to be read for the feast of the metropolitans.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7.14">
                           <locus from="147v" to="149v"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1100Anapho">ʾAkkʷateta qʷǝrbān za-ʾǝgziʾǝna ʾIyasus Krǝstos</title>
                           <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                              ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ጸሎቱ፡ ፈትቶ፡ በል፨ ወካዕበ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ናስተበቍዖ፡</supplied> ከመ፡ የሀበነ፡ 
                              በበረከተ፨ ንንሣእ፡ ዘ<del rend="expunctuated">እ</del>ቅዱስ፡ ምሥጢር፡ ጽንዓተ፡ ለነ፡ የሀበነ፨ ወኢመነሂ፡ እምውስቴትነ፡ ወኢያርስሕ፡ አላ፡ ለኵሉ፡ 
                              ተድላሆሙ፡ ይረሲ፡ ለእለ፤ <sic>ይትሜጠው፡</sic> ንሥአተ፡ ቅዱስ፤ ምስጢር፡ ዘሥጋሁ፡ ወደሙ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ዘኵሎ፤ ይእኅዝ፤ እግዚአብሔር፤ አምላክነ፤ 
                              ይ<supplied reason="explanation">ብል</supplied>፡ ዲ<supplied reason="explanation">ያቆን</supplied>፡ ጸልዩ። ይ<supplied reason="explanation">ብል</supplied>፡ 
